Interface Credential

  • All Superinterfaces:
    CredentialTypes, com.vmware.vapi.bindings.Service
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CredentialStub

    public interface Credential
extends com.vmware.vapi.bindings.Service, CredentialTypes
    The Credential interface provides methods to add a credential for external key management service(s). This interface was added in vSphere API 7.0.0.0.
